# Solver testdata directory

Copy config.json.sample to config.json and edit if needed but if you are not 
changing the tests then there is no need to edit this file.

Copy api-key.yaml.sample to api-key.yaml. Edit to add your base64 encoded
NS1 API Key. This populates the apiKeySecretRef. Make sure to use the test 
NS1 account API key which can be obtained from 1password.
